description	"Purge Trooper ^3[Reworked]

Dexterous Melee/gunner hybrids who can spec into anti-Jedi tools, damage protection, Electro-Weapon upgrades, and advanced mobility options.

^2Weaponry:
- Melee
- Electrosaber
-- Saber Defense (1)
-- No Blaster Block
-- Applies Shock On Hit
> Imperial Electrostaff (Staff)
-- +15% Attack Speed
-- +3% Knockback
-- -6% Reach
> Double Electrobatons (Dual)
-- +10% Attack Speed
-- +2% Knockback
-- -60% Reach

^8Attributes:
- Stamina (0)

^3Abilities:
- Sprint ^3[CS1]"